---
title: Lamb Rump & Grilled Capsicum Tacos with Charred Corn, Avocado & Pickled Radish
description: Looks like our tacos are evolving into their ultimate phase! These new and improved tacos come equipped with tender lamb
rump, cooked to perfection, pickled radish, avocado and for their finishing move - smokey grilled capsicum. These are some
seriously S-class tacos.
